  "title": "Retail Assistant | 5 days | No experience required",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a friendly and customer-oriented Retail Assistant to provide excellent customer service, supporting daily store operations, and achieve sales targets.<br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Greet and assist customers in a friendly and professional manner</p></li><li><p>Promote and recommend products to customers</p></li><li><p>Handle cashiering duties, including payment processing and POS operations</p></li><li><p>Replenish stock and ensure merchandise is properly displayed</p></li><li><p>Maintain store cleanliness and visual standards</p></li><li><p>Handle customer enquiries, feedback, and basic complaints</p></li><li><p>Support daily opening and closing of the store<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Customer-focused with good communication skills</p></li><li><p>Able to work shifts, weekends, and public holidays</p></li><li><p>Team player with a positive attitude<br /></p></li></ul><p>Suitable applicants who fit certain requirements may be offered other positions too!<br /></p><p></p><p>Interested applicants please click apply now!<br /></p><p>Hey Rocket Pte. Ltd. (EA 21C0816)<br /></p><p>Jerlynn Pang (R25142244)</p>",
